title: Trae Tha Truth &ndash; I Am King  mixtape
description:
Trae Tha Truth releases his I Am King mixtape. A 20-track project featuring guest appearances from Diddy, Jeezy, T.I., Snoop Dogg, Meek Mill, Wiz Khalifa, Big K.R.I.T., Jadakiss, Yo Gotti and lots more. Beat Bully, Honorable C-Note, Dun Deal, Jahlil Beats, and League of Starz provide production.

01. Trae Tha Truth - Intro [Prod. By B.o.B] 
02. Trae Tha Truth - Hold Up (Feat. Diddy, Young Jeezy & T.I.) [Prod. By Beat Bully] 
03. Trae Tha Truth - Stay Trill (Bill Collector) (Feat. Krayzie Bone & Roscoe Dash) [Prod. By Honorable C Note] 
04. Trae Tha Truth - F*cked Up (Feat. Lil Reese) [Prod. By Kaleon & Don Lee] 
05. Trae Tha Truth - I Am King (Interlude) [Prod. By Watson The Great]
06. Trae Tha Truth - Shit Crazy (Feat. D Dash Bo) [Prod. By London On The Track] 
07. Trae Tha Truth - Dark Angel (Feat. Kevin Gates) 
08. Trae Tha Truth - Driven (Feat. Lupe Fiasco & Poo Bear MDMA) [Prod. By Bizness Boi]
09. Trae Tha Truth - Street Miracle [Prod. By Dun Deal] 
10. Trae Tha Truth - Old School (Feat. Baby Houston & Snoop Dogg) [Prod. By Trackbangas] 
11. Trae Tha Truth - Ride Wit Me (Feat. Meek Mill & T.I.) [Prod. By Boi-1da]
12. Trae Tha Truth - Floyd Mayweather (Interlude) [Prod. By Watson The Great] 
13. Trae Tha Truth - I Am King [Prod. By Jahlil Beats] 
14. Trae Tha Truth - 1 Up (Feat. Lil Boss, Wiz Khalifa & Jadakiss) [Prod. By League Of Starz] 
15. Trae Tha Truth - Hallelujah (Feat. Jay'Ton & Yo Gotti) [Prod. By Trackbangas] 
16. Trae Tha Truth - Halo (Feat. Tory Lanez) [Prod. By V Don]
17. Trae Tha Truth - Ghetto Life (Feat. Dougie D & Da Brat) [Prod. By Honorable C Note] 
18. Trae Tha Truth - I Believe (Feat. Mama C & Big K.R.I.T.) [Prod. By Mr Inkredible]
19. Trae Tha Truth - Ugly Truth (Feat. B.o.B) [Prod. By Bizness Boi]
20. Trae Tha Truth - Outro (Family No Family) (Feat. Tasha Catour) [Prod. By Daniel Few]
